Package org.neo4j.internal.kernel.api

Interface CursorFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultPooledCursors, DefaultThreadSafeCursors, StubCursorFactory
    public interface CursorFactory
    Allocates Cursors. To read data from the Kernel, Cursors are needed. A Cursor factory let's the Kernel consumer allocate all types of cursors, which can then be reused for multiple read operations.
